These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
Game: monopoly, whist, bridge, snooker
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, family, mystery
Birthday: february, april, may, december
Beverage: cola, lemonade, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
 1. Birthday:april is not to the right of Birthday:february##8
 2. Beverage:cola is not to the left of Beverage:cola##8
 3. Beverage:iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
 4. Birthday:february is not to the left of Birthday:december##8
 5. Beverage:cola is not to the right of Beverage:cola##8
 6. Movie-Genre:family is on the right of Birthday:december##1
 7. Game:whist is somewhere to the right of Game:monopoly##5
 8. Movie-Genre:mystery is between Beverage:lemonade and Birthday:april##2
 9. Beverage:iced-tea == Movie-Genre:family##1
10. Beverage:iced-tea is on the right of Game:snooker##1
11. Game:bridge is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:animation##3
12. Game:snooker is somewhere to the right of Game:whist##5
13. Movie-Genre:family is not to the left of Beverage:iced-tea##8
14. Game:whist == Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
15. Game:whist != Birthday:april##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game         | monopoly     | whist   | snooker | bridge |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Birthday         | april  | may  | december  | february |
| Beverage     | cola    | hot-chocolate | lemonade     | iced-tea    |

